    "description": "Hokko Chemical Industry Co., Ltd., together with subsidiaries, manufactures and sells crop protection and fine chemicals products in Japan and internationally. The company operates through three segments: Agricultural Chemicals Business, Fine Chemicals Business, and Textile Materials Business. It offers insecticides, fungicides, herbicides, plant growth regulators, pesticides, and related products; resin additives, pharmaceutical and agrochemical intermediates, raw materials for electronics components, functional polymers, organic catalysts, raw materials for functional inorganic materials, fine ceramics, raw materials for agricultural chemicals and artificial intelligence in the electronic materials field, preservatives, antifouling, antiseptic and antifungal agents, epoxy resin curing accelerators and related products; and textile materials. The company also provides raw resin materials, such as photoresist monomers and curing accelerators for epoxy molding compounds, semiconductor encapsulants; and electronic materials. Hokko Chemical Industry Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1950 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
